  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The model was revised in early 2026 to incorporate updated impeller geometry tolerances; however, the primary validation dataset retains a dataVintage of 2025-09-15, predating the modelRevisionDate of 2026-01-10. Re-validation against the revised model build is described as planned but has not been completed, leaving an epistemic gap between the current model and the evidence base.",
