      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements collected on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at five operating points. Used as primary spatial velocity validation evidence. dataVintage reflects the experimental campaign completion date, which predates the January 2026 model revision that updated impeller gap tolerances. Re-validation against the revised model is planned but not yet executed.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-09-15T00:00:00Z"
