      "description": "In-vitro modified index of hemolysis measurements collected at matching operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal pump. Collected November 2025, after PIV campaign but still prior to the January 2026 model revision.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-11-20T00:00:00Z"
    }
