      "acceptanceCriteria": "Blood analog fluid characterization (viscosity, density, hematocrit distribution) must be documented with traceability to measurement standards for all validation samples.",
      "rationale": "Fluid characterization records available for viscosity and density. Hematocrit distribution across test samples not fully documented; sample-to-sample variability not propagated into validation uncertainty. Flagged as epistemic gap."
