      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency assessment mapping validation experiment input parameters to COU device input parameters, with documented uncertainty in the mapping.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency mapping performed informally. No formal uncertainty propagation through the mapping from FDA generic pump test conditions to target VAD operating conditions. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
