    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that all seven assessed factors demonstrate progressive evidence and the six not-assessed factors are documented as planned work items with identified owners and target completion dates. The team noted that the primary validation datasets (PIV campaign completed September 2025 and hemolysis bench study completed November 2025) predate the January 2026 model revision; re-validation is planned for Q2 2026 prior to regulatory submission. The team considered this gap acceptable for the current internal milestone but flagged it as a condition of acceptance requiring resolution before final regulatory filing.",
